1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to the Administrative Procedure Act; to amend
2 section 84-920, Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska; to create a
3 review process for rules and regulations; to require reports as
4 prescribed; to harmonize provisions; and to repeal the original
5 section.
6 Be it enacted by the people of the State of Nebraska,
-1-

