1 (a) Affects the health, safety, or welfare of the public;
2 (b) Is time sensitive; or
3 (c) Is subject to state or federal statutory deadlines.
4 Sec. 2. Section 84-920, Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska, is
5 amended to read:
6 84-920 Sections 84-901 to 84-920 and section 1 of this act, the
7 Occupational Board Reform Act, and the Personal Privacy Protection Act
8 shall be known and may be cited as the Administrative Procedure Act.
9 Sec. 3. Original section 84-920, Reissue Revised Statutes of
10 Nebraska, is repealed.
